          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/By authors/ In the Aarhus and Jyvaskyla measurements",
                "the irradiations were performed in vacuum and the",
                "beam was dumped away from the target. In the Turku",
                "measurements the target was mounted directly on a",
                "graphite beam-stop just after a thin steel window which",
                "terminated the beam line.",
                "/By authors/ The results Th-232(p,gamma)Pa-233 still",
                "had to be corrected for the effects of neutron capture",
                "in the target of neutrons produced inside the target",
                "volume. The contributing processes are the (p,n),",
                " (p,2n), (p,3n) and (p,f) reactions on Th-232.",
                " A correction for the influence of the (p,xn) reactions",
                "was calculated with the assumption of a compound",
                "nucleus energy spectrum of the neutrons and with the",
                "cross sections given in Celler et al.(see MONIT-REF)."
              ]
            }
          ],
