          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/By authors/ The relative fission cross sections were",
                "obtained via a normalization to the K-shell ionization",
                "cross sections used also by Celler et.al (see",
                "MONIT-REF). The resulting relative fission yield",
                "curve was transformed into an absolute excitation",
                "function by normalization to the excitation function",
                "of Kurcewicz et al., see REL-REF."
